name: Registre RGPD CVMH
author: CVMH solutions

sections.installation:
1. Unzip the plugin and upload the “cvmh-registre-rgpd” folder to your “/wp-content/plugins/” directory
  2. Activate the plugin through the “Plugins” administration page in WordPress
  3. Use the shortcode or the widget
  4. Enjoy.
sections.description:
Extension expliquant le registre RGPD pour les clients CVMH

Looking for a WordPress agency? Contact us: agence web WordPress

How to uninstall Registre RGPD CVMH

To uninstall Registre RGPD CVMH, you just have to de-activate the plugin from the plugins list.
